<div class="concept">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row mt-3">
      <!-- Left Column (Our Commitment to Your Trust) -->
      <div class="col-md-5 mt-4 mb-3">
        <div class="content-border">
          <h2>Our Commitment to Your Trust</h2>
          <%= image_tag 'handshake.webp', style: "width: 100%; height: 100px; object-fit: cover;", alt: "ex", class: "me-3" %>
          <div class="content mb-4">
            <p>
              At LuxeHaven, we understand that trust is the cornerstone of a successful marketplace. That's why we prioritize your confidence in every transaction and product listed on our platform.<br>
              Every item submitted to our marketplace undergoes a rigorous validation process before it becomes available to you.<br>
              Our cutting-edge bot, equipped with advanced algorithms and machine learning capabilities, meticulously reviews each submission to ensure it meets our high standards of quality and authenticity. This automated system is designed to detect any discrepancies, ensuring that only the best and most reliable products make it to our marketplace.
              By leveraging this technology, we can offer you a secure and trustworthy shopping experience, knowing that each item has been thoroughly vetted. <br>
              Your satisfaction and safety are our top priorities, and we continuously work to maintain the highest level of integrity in our marketplace.
              Thank you for placing your trust in us. We are committed to delivering a platform where you can shop with confidence, knowing that every product has been carefully validated for your peace of mind.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag 'logo_home', style: "width: 100%; height: 400px; object-fit: cover;", alt: "ex", class: "mt-4" %>
      </div>
      <!-- Right Column (Why Rent over Buy?, Going Global Soon!, Curated Collection of Extravagance) -->
      <div class="col-md-7 mt-4">
        <!-- Why Rent over Buy? -->
        <div class="content-border mb-4">
          <div class="bg-content">
            <h2>Why Rent over Buy?</h2>
            <p>
              Luxury is about experiencing the extraordinary.<br>
              Renting allows you to enjoy a diverse range of premium products without the constraints of ownership.<br>
              LuxeHaven provides you with the flexibility to select the perfect items for each event, ensuring that you always have access to the latest and most coveted pieces.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag 'car_driving.webp', style: "width: 100%; height: 235px; max-height: 500px; object-fit: cover;", alt:"" %>
        </div>
        <!-- Going Global Soon! -->
        <div class="content-border mb-4">
          <h2>Exciting News: Going Global Soon!</h2>
          <p>
            We’re thrilled to share that LuxeHaven will soon be expanding our services to international markets!
            We’re committed to bringing our exceptional services to customers around the world, and we can’t wait to serve you wherever you are.
            Stay tuned for updates as we work on making our platform available internationally. Thank you for your continued support and trust in us. We look forward to connecting with you globally!
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Curated Collection of Extravagance -->
        <div class="content-border mb-4">
          <div class="content d-flex align-items-start">
            <%= image_tag 'ex_img.webp', style: "width: 150px; height: 430px; object-fit: cover;", alt: "ex", class: "me-3" %>
            <div>
              <h2>Curated Collection of Extravagance</h2>
              <p>
                Our carefully curated selection features the epitome of elegance and sophistication.<br>
                From exquisite watches that keep more than just time, to tailored suits that define your style, our offerings are designed for those who demand the best.<br>
                Step into luxury with our stunning range of high-end cars, or add a touch of glamour with our handpicked jewels, each piece telling a story of timeless beauty.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- End of Right Column -->
    </div>
    <!-- End of Row -->
  </div>
  <!-- End of Container -->
</div>
